title: Turkmenistan Total External Debt
description: External Debt in Turkmenistan increased to 5636041.54 USD Thousand in 2020 from 567628.38 USD Thousand in 2019. External Debt in Turkmenistan averaged 1257466.30 USD Thousand from 1993 until 2020, reaching an all time high of 5636041.54 USD Thousand in 2020 and a record low of 276435 USD Thousand in 1993. This page provides - Turkmenistan External Debt- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: SESRIC - The Statistical, Economic & Social Res. & Training Centre for Islamic Countries
